```bash
#!/data/data/com.termux/files/usr/bin/bash

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🌸 DESFCITA BOT • SISTEMA DE INICIO AVANZADO 🌸
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════

clear

# ─── Colores ────────────────────────────────────
PINK="\e[38;5;213m"
PURPLE="\e[38;5;141m"
BLUE="\e[38;5;81m"
GREEN="\e[38;5;120m"
YELLOW="\e[38;5;228m"
RED="\e[38;5;203m"
RESET="\e[0m"
BOLD="\e[1m"

# ─── Función escribir lento ─────────────────────
typewriter () {
  text="$1"
  delay="${2:-0.03}"
  for (( i=0; i<${#text}; i++ )); do
    echo -ne "${text:$i:1}"
    sleep $delay
  done
  echo
}

# ─── Header bonito ──────────────────────────────
echo -e "${PINK}${BOLD}"
echo "╔══════════════════════════════════════════════╗"
echo "║        🌸 DESFCITA • BOT SYSTEM 🌸            ║"
echo "║        ✨ Inicio Avanzado Ultra ✨             ║"
echo "╚══════════════════════════════════════════════╝"
echo -e "${RESET}"
sleep 0.6

typewriter "${PURPLE}➤ Preparando entorno mágico..." 0.04
sleep 0.5
typewriter "${BLUE}➤ Sincronizando módulos estelares..." 0.04
sleep 0.5
typewriter "${GREEN}➤ Despertando al bot..." 0.04
sleep 0.6

echo ""

# ─── Barra de carga ─────────────────────────────
echo -e "${YELLOW}${BOLD}   🚀 CARGANDO SISTEMA${RESET}\n"

BAR_LENGTH=28

for i in $(seq 0 $BAR_LENGTH); do
  FILLED=$(printf "%0.s▰" $(seq 1 $i))
  EMPTY=$(printf "%0.s▱" $(seq 1 $((BAR_LENGTH - i))))
  PERCENT=$(( i * 100 / BAR_LENGTH ))

  printf "\r${PINK}[${GREEN}%s${PURPLE}%s${PINK}] ${BLUE}%3d%% ✨${RESET}" "$FILLED" "$EMPTY" "$PERCENT"
  sleep 0.08
done

echo -e "\n\n${GREEN}${BOLD}✔ Sistema listo"
echo -e "${PINK}✔ Conexión establecida"
echo -e "${PURPLE}✔ Todo se ve precioso 🌸${RESET}"
sleep 1

# ─── Lanzar bot ─────────────────────────────────
echo ""
typewriter "${BLUE}✨ Ejecutando bot.py ... buena suerte 🍀" 0.03
sleep 0.6
echo ""

python bot.py
```
